---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Enablement Engineering" description="Dylan Isaac, founder of Enablement Engineering. Building AI systems that extend human capability without hiding their reasoning.">
	<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Opening -->
			<div class="mb-16">
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start gap-8">
					<img
						src="/me-square.jpg"
						alt="Dylan Isaac"
						class="w-40 h-40 rounded-2xl object-cover flex-shrink-0"
					/>
					<div>
						<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">
							About
						</h1>
						<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
							I'm Dylan Isaac, founder of Enablement Engineering.
						</p>
						<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
							I build <a href="/definitions/glass-box" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">glass-box AI systems</a> that extend human capability‚Äîsystems that can stand up to audit while genuinely empowering the people who use them.
						</p>
						<p class="text-lg text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
							I believe <a href="/writing/epistemological-translator" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">accessibility work is alignment work</a>‚Äîthe accessibility community has decades of experience with problems AI researchers are only now addressing.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<hr class="border-neutral-200 mb-16" />

			<!-- Background -->
			<div class="mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">Background</h2>
				<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-neutral-700">
					<p>
						Former <strong>Lead AI Engineer at Deque Systems</strong>, where I built <a href="https://www.deque.com/axe/assistant/" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">axe Assistant</a> and developed foundational approaches to AI-generated accessibility content.
					</p>
					<p>
						A decade of full-stack engineering experience, with deep expertise in accessibility, agentic systems, and the intersection of the two.
					</p>
					<p>
						Currently building the <a href="/work/uic-equalify" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">Equalify PDF to Semantic Markup Converter</a> with UIC Digital Accessibility Services‚Äîtransforming inaccessible academic PDFs into adaptive web experiences at scale. Presenting this work at <strong>CSUN 2026</strong>.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<hr class="border-neutral-200 mb-16" />

			<!-- Philosophy -->
			<div class="mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">Philosophy</h2>
				<div class="space-y-8">
					<div class="card-base p-6 off-kilter-0-5">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Ladders, not walls.</h3>
						<p class="text-neutral-600">
							Technology should extend what people can do, not create dependency.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="card-base p-6 off-kilter-neg-0-5">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Mirrors, not slot machines.</h3>
						<p class="text-neutral-600">
							Systems should reflect user intention, not capture attention.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="card-base p-6 off-kilter-0-5">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Glass box, not black box.</h3>
						<p class="text-neutral-600">
							Reasoning should be visible and auditable, especially when compliance matters.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				</div>

			<hr class="border-neutral-200 mb-16" />

			<!-- Beyond Work -->
			<div class="mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">Beyond Work</h2>
				<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-neutral-700">
					<p>
						I live in Buffalo, NY with my wife and partner Kaitlin, our dog Basil, and our kitten Corni. ‚ù§Ô∏èü¶¨üíô
					</p>
					<p>
						I'm drawn to tools that give people leverage‚Äîand I'm happiest turning messy reality into systems that make sense.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<hr class="border-neutral-200 mb-16" />

			<!-- CTA -->
			<div class="text-center">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">
					Get in Touch
				</h2>
				<a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold bg-accent-500 text-secondary-900 hover:bg-accent-600 h-12 px-10 no-underline">
					Start a Conversation
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
